Package it.unipr.barbato.Model.Message

Class MessageHandlerImpl

java.lang.Object
it.unipr.barbato.Model.Message.MessageHandlerImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Handler, MessageHandler
public class MessageHandlerImpl extends Object implements Handler, MessageHandler
The MessageHandlerImpl class implements the Handler and MessageHandler interfaces and provides functionality for handling JMS messages.

Vincenzo Barbato 345728
